### ============================================
### COMPUTER SCIENCE COURSE API TESTS
### ============================================

### 1. CREATE COURSE 1 (Foundation - Programming)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseCode": "CSC101",
  "name": "Introduction to Programming",
  "type": "Foundation",
  "credits": 4
}

###

