### 8. GET ALL COURSES
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses

###

### 9. GET COURSE SUMMARY (PART A)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/summary

###

### 10. GET SINGLE COURSE (ID = 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/1

###

### 11. UPDATE COURSE (ID = 1)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseCode": "CSC101",
  "name": "Advanced Introduction to Programming",
  "type": "Foundation",
  "credits": 4
}

###

### 12. DELETE COURSE (ID = 2)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/courses/2

###

### 13. VERIFY DELETE (Get all courses again)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses

###

### 14. TEST VALIDATION - Invalid Course Code Format
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseCode": "CSC99",
  "name": "Test Course",
  "type": "Foundation",
  "credits": 4
}

###

### 15. TEST VALIDATION - Invalid Type
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseCode": "CSC999",
  "name": "Test Course",
  "type": "Master",
  "credits": 4
}

###

### 16. TEST VALIDATION - Credits Too High
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseCode": "CSC509",
  "name": "Test Course",
  "type": "Undergraduate",
  "credits": 10
}

###

### 17. TEST VALIDATION - Missing Required Fields
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instructor": "Dr. Test"
}